flowchart TD
    A["**Idle**<br/>· Not initialized<br/>· Waits for Init"]
    B["**Inited**<br/>· Driver and config are ready<br/>· Can start connection flow"]
    C["**Started**<br/>· Wi-Fi is started<br/>· Can initiate connection"]
    D["**Connected**<br/>· AP is connected<br/>· Provides network capability"]

    A -->|"Init"| B
    B -->|"Start"| C
    C -->|"Connect"| D
    D -->|"Disconnect"| C
    C -->|"Stop"| B
    D -->|"Stop"| B
    B -->|"Deinit"| A
